<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The setRequired method should exists for the Zend_Dojo_Form_Element_ValidationTextBox and use setDijitParam('required', 'true').
It is useful for the form validation of dojo.</p>

<p>Here's a working patch :</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
